# ── NEVER PUBLISH ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# This folder is the single source of truth for the live site.
# Everything listed here stays in the folder but is NOT pushed online.
#
# Why each is excluded:
#   sources/   — third-party copyrighted PDFs + the homestead image
#                (link-only until the artist grants permission)
#   *.md       — internal working docs: raw material, other people's
#                testimonials, personal/origin notes, essay drafts, HANDOFF
#   .claude/   — local tooling/config
#   .DS_Store  — macOS cruft
#
# Anything NOT listed here (index.html, lessons.html, writing/*.html)
# goes live exactly as it is in this folder.

sources/
*.md
.claude/
.DS_Store

# safety: never resurrect a duplicate publish copy
public/
